org.apache.james.protocols.lib.handler

Interface HandlersPackage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.apache.james.protocols.api.handler.ProtocolHandler
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CoreCmdHandlerLoader, CoreCmdHandlerLoader, CoreCmdHandlerLoader, JMXHandlersLoader, JMXHandlersLoader, JMXHandlersLoader

    public interface HandlersPackage
extends org.apache.james.protocols.api.handler.ProtocolHandler
    Provides a mean to bundle a set of handlers (defined by their classnames) within a single object. This is used for the default set of CoreCommands.
